    <stitle>Spanish - Gu&#237;a para Localizaci&#243;n de Fallas del Sistema El&#233;ctrico - 3200, 4200, 4300, 4400,
        7300, 7400, 7500, 8500, 8600 - ANTILOCK AIR BRAKE SYSTEM WITH TRACTION CONTROL: BENDIX - 9200, 9300 and 9400 -
        INSTALLATION
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>INSTALLATION</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="0">
            <title>M21 MODULATOR VALVE</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install all air line fittings and plugs making certain thread sealing material does not
                    enter the valve.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install the assembled valve on the vehicle.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Reconnect both air lines to the valve using the identification made during valve
                    removal.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Reconnect the electrical connector to the M-21.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">After installing the valve, test all air fittings for excessive leakage and tighten as
                    needed.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
